verbose_text: Compared to WT CD45.2 + BM mixed with WT CD45.1 + CD45.2 + BM chimera (WT : WT mice), Gpr183 -/- CD45.2 + BM mixed with WT CD45.1 + CD45.2 + BM chimera (Gpr183 -/- : WT mice) had significantly reduced ratios of CD45.2 + ILC3s to CD45.1 + CD45.2 + ILC3s in the SI.
